        <mxCell id="lwDhFy6XJbLUevfUC_to-20" parent="lwDhFy6XJbLUevfUC_to-1" style="shape=partialRectangle;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;right=0;top=0;bottom=0;fillColor=none;routingCenterX=-0.5;" value="" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="411" width="226" x="413" y="363" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xKBuqy8DKaJkAhcU9lFn-9" parent="lwDhFy6XJbLUevfUC_to-1" style="shape=image;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;labelBackgroundColor=default;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/png,;" value="`" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="273" width="433.32" x="413" y="367" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="xKBuqy8DKaJkAhcU9lFn-4" parent="lwDhFy6XJbLUevfUC_to-1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;spacing=0;horizontal=1;textShadow=0;autosizeText=1;imageAspect=1;resizeWidth=0;autosize=0;fontSize=6;" value="&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 13px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;• During testing, CPU and memory stress caused rapid metric fluctuations.&lt;br&gt;• Kubernetes automatically maintained service availability during pod restart.&lt;br&gt;• Prometheus retained continuous visibility even when application restarted.&lt;br&gt;• Recovery actions changed environment state without manual intervention.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="128" width="416" x="9" y="811" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
