        <mxCell id="vaaSCTO8l6Lg665QWm2X-21" parent="vaaSCTO8l6Lg665QWm2X-1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;rounded=0;spacing=0;horizontal=1;textShadow=0;autosizeText=1;imageAspect=1;resizeWidth=0;autosize=0;fontSize=15;" value="• DevOps engineer monitors system health and recovery success&lt;br&gt;• Software developer performs stress testing using CPU and memory endpoints&lt;br&gt;• System administrator configures Kubernetes deployment and permissions&lt;br&gt;• End users continue task operations without noticing failures&lt;br&gt;• Analyzer perform autonomous decisons&amp;nbsp; without waiting for human commands" vertex="1">
